    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's been a few days so i thought the bedding in would be mostly done by now. the sound is really piercing though, almost like metal on metal. i'm worried i might have messed something up during the install. what's the next best thing to check to make sure it's not a serious mechanical failure?",
